title: Jin Leads by 1 Into Final Round of Asia-Pacific Amateur
text:
Published By: NYTimes Golf - Today 
Jin Cheng of China pitched to a half-foot on the par-5 18th and made birdie for a 1-under 69 to take a one-stroke lead over two Australians ...
